1. Want to be able to add CLA
	* systheme [THEME] [FLAGS]
	* -s simulation     Simulation mode, no files are overwritten, turns on verbose.
	* -v verbose        Print out progress report.
	* -q quiet          Surpress all output.
	* -b backup         Backup any overwritten files in ~/.systheme_backups directory
	* -c confirm        Prompt user for confirmation before each file is overwritten
	* -h

